Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是那個\N想成為乙HiME的女孩吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.57,0:00:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係，就讓她進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這麼辦如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以真白即位典禮餘興節目的名目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她跟妮娜比劃一場舞鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏的人可以留在學校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸的就離開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點子不賴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我打
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她比劃一場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白，妳覺得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.90,0:00:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要聽你的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的提議還是不算數
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一妮娜輸了的話\N那我可就傷腦筋了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟她將來\N可能會成為我的乙HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩個就打一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在即位典禮上\N為了我而起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心悸動無法平息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿盈內心 開始散放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會如此不安呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法控制的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不禁落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日一定會抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算中途受挫也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能踏出小小的一步 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嶄新的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:03:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第3話 首·次·經·驗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好固定住喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能掉到客人們頭上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是大致上的警備方針
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的城堡已經變成那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能辦出一場會讓凪\N和其他國王見笑的典禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要準備得萬無一失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外關於那場舞鬥的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在時間和會場佈置預算上\N都相當吃緊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內務大臣希望\N能夠重新評估一番
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪能做出到現在才說要中止\N這種丟臉的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主一旦碰到凪殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會發怒\N然後被牽著鼻子走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會痛或有哪裡怪怪的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然跟奈米機械很合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能得在床上躺好幾天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃，那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說跟那個叫奈米機械的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是在身體裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注射能使武具和舞鬥服物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且提高肌力\N和治癒能力的極微小機械啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:05:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個加爾德羅貝\N還保有這種技術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是科學的神秘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子我就可以穿上\N那個帥氣的服裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳沒有戴GEM\N所以只有一次機會就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的學生\N每個人都有戴耳環對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫做GEM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責控制奈米機械
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，請幫我也戴一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等妳正式當上本校學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在我打贏妮娜之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要先保留了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧那個調皮的公主\N中了凪大公的言語陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整件事情變得更複雜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的眉頭都皺起來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣就只能順著局勢走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜可沒有好對付到\N臨時抱佛腳就可以勝過她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想想下一步該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生們也因為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了這個消息\N而變得不太安分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜賭上退學，要跟那個\N在校園裸奔的女孩舞鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是在\N真白公主的即位典禮上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩要是贏了\N好像就可以入學耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣？太詐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情太亂七八糟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎？我覺得很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是妮娜的話\N應該可以輕鬆得勝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊…是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯真是愛操心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為，自從決定要舞鬥之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜好像就很緊繃的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮依娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:06:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會在各國來賓面前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侮辱父親與殿下名譽的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要想太多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要拿出平常的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就不可能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那女孩是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以打贏她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是妳不贏我會很頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了，我會盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我女兒啊，妮依娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下一時興起\N可讓我們手忙腳亂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為星星的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得見明日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心愛的人兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻，剛才那首歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又叫我螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼辦法，很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這個了，你在這幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳才是在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話，就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在身體習慣奈米機械之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們要我安分一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的想跟妮娜進行舞鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜很強喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個第一次披上舞鬥服的人\N根本沒有勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已經下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要當乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳真的知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為乙HiME究竟是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是妳贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會毀掉熬過嚴格訓練\N才能進這學校就讀的妮娜的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的夢想真的有這個價值嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆總是對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼都好，要有夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了夢想就不要逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要中途氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那時候我並不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是來到這裡\N看過乙HiME戰鬥之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種“就是這個～”的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我好不容易找到的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算是亂來也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要拼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再多說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就儘管追逐妳的夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你多說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那首歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個？是婆婆常唱的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是很古老的搖籃曲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌詞是完整的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道剛剛那段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是媽媽常常唱的搖籃曲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我告訴妳一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道歌詞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有點走音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勸妳不要\N在別人面前唱歌比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了以防萬一…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是先著手下一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想看現場喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後再去問姊姊們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留姊姊也在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子老師，請讓我們看電視
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，宿舍也有電視吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法靜下來專心看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我不會要妳白白讓我看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在古董店找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿來用在老師的寶貝上如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有年份的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以讓其他學生知道喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡迪亞帝國\N阿格斯十四世皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及“瑰麗的縞瑪瑙”\N菲亞·葛羅斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我為您帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是負責引導\N愛瑞斯大總統閣下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎會晚點到的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是豪華
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會難得，好好欣賞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是在乙HiME之中\N很有名氣的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個白衣的姊姊是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們是二年級
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在珍珠乙HiME中\N成績名列前三名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗稱“三和弦”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很榮幸地能夠協助典禮進行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往這邊看了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始看戲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有一場\N賭上入學資格的舞鬥要打
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真悠哉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿爾泰公國大公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪·戴·阿爾泰殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝你給我機會，殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳叫愛莉卡對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家的妮娜\N壓根沒有打算要輸給妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要當乙HiME的人\N就得要有這種氣魄嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這場即位典禮\N還真是場鬧劇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白到底是不是真正的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都還不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下，在這裡講這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都假裝忘記了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14年前的那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白公主妳好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命留下來看家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳正經一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白·布蘭·杜·溫德布倫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝是否有覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願意為國家犧牲個人幸福\N為人民盡心盡力呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，便授與汝此頂王冠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給予新王祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用我的GEM控制妳的舞鬥服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要動手了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要表現出一場\N配得上我即位典禮的舞鬥喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是為了這個而給妳機會的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼從現在起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了慶祝我即位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將進行一場\N乙HiME候補生的舞鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，哪邊會贏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩邊都輸了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照理來說是妮娜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能不合常理？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是有這種感覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們就為了我好好起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是乙HiME的舞鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，愛莉卡也一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是被那黑函擺佈的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲人士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別把我跟黑團的人混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自黑色山谷的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在淑女面前講這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不識相的人\N還是請你嚐嚐茶泡飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬌嫣的紫水晶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很夠份量當我的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡很拼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以外行人來說…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳是\N“蒼天的青玉”的繼承人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，就是因為這樣才更…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才更不能輸！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.23,0:21:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆她說過…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是死心就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還想打？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的…挺了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好本事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:21:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.19,0:22:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.59,0:22:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:22:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.65,0:23:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.43,0:23:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次是第4話嗎\N（火焰轉學生！！)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.78,0:23:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種不祥的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為夏樹在學生時代\N曾經把內衣…
